Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反复思考之后 蕾孤身前往煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.29,0:02:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追赶她的酷等人与煌珠猎人卧鲁克斯再次相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他只把搭档吉露露当作工具使唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷再次被激怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.16,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吉露露却\N奋不顾身地保护对她恶言相向的卧鲁克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠与同契者的关系真是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深铭刻在内心深处之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷等人继续启程去追赶蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.37,0:02:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在艾波赫利大陆\N建起了我们ChaosChoir的前线基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在增援到来之前保护好基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不准向任何人泄漏我们的真实身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果附近出现可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他们干掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已在数日前击退了进犯的守护翼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定他们断气了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可爱的玩偶 我是不喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不允许再次失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个基地必须好好守住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是连这也做不到的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们想成为真正的煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五唱 大风车的村庄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.89,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥丽佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.06,0:05:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把飞机...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放着好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧也要适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不乖乖听我们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就让你吃点苦头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会打破这堵墙让风车再次转起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.84,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种地方耽搁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点找蕾的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去这城市的医院看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医院干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个以前照顾过我们的守护翼的前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在几天前受了重伤住院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们就去看望他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就要去找蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿让我下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙威鲁德前辈是为执行特别任务而被派遣到这地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.92,0:06:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他知道一些盯上蕾的敌人的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但害你吓了一跳还要让你帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一个人站在那种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样下去的话是转不起来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座风车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有那堵石墙的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在几个月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的那帮流氓袭击了村庄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强迫我们造了那堵石墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人虽然在一开始也有过抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙总在关键时刻使用奇怪的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打不过他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后大家都听他们的摆布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是用那风车抽取地下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输送到村里及田里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自从有了那堵墙之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风的通路就被挡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田地完全干枯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连日常饮用水也供应困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要破坏那堵墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方的建筑物\N都是以顶上的五角形拱心石为中心建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏了那里整堵墙就会倒塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那堵石墙也是用相同的方法建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只要坐着这东西飞到那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏了那块石头的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这飞机是由靳做的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又去胡闹了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你乱弄一气惹得他们来报复怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光等着风是不会吹过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不通过自己的力量让风车转起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没用的 放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了忍耐没其他办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿沙威鲁德前辈的伤势好转 能跟我们说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 是希丝卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.74,0:08:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.58,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在这里见到姐姐 夏尔罗真是太高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和龙也好多年不见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别站在门口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来 快进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you 帮了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让蕾住在我家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.15,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 得赶紧把这东西修好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定要破坏那堵墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.55,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 饭做好后就给你送来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样 谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你身体安康 我暂且放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.82,0:09:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈居然受这么重的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说最近在这地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个神秘组织在对抗守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去调查它的底细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查之后 发现了一处疑为敌人前线基地的设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入探个究竟时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到敌人伏击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同契之后很快就被打得落花流水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是千钧一发之际
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总算是逃了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个敌人的组织的名字是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.88,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 组织的名字好像是叫ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾有个自称是ChaosChoir的特工的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击过酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.86,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说要抓蕾的人正在这附近转悠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想 他是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫酷德·望·朱鲁爱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是七煌宝树的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.39,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们也得告辞了 得马上去追他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 龙威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于ChaosChoir这个敌人还是再多了解一些为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出事啊 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很鲁莽吧 由靳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.00,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那么小的飞机想要转动那么大的风车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但错的事他绝对不会去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾也认识这样的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.02,0:12:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想转动那个风车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风车就交给你了 奥丽佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.92,0:15:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...和我在一起的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定就算那样也要和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.22,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.04,0:17:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的是从天使守护队总部逃出来的七煌宝树吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是煌珠吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是ChaosChoir的拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来救我们的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点和我们同契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些家伙干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只不过是需要你们的身体而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.88,0:18:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比抓住七煌宝树更重要的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵引之线{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此倾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我共颂念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息相应{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕飞旋之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远相随{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤诚之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕飞扬之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜藏于暗夜之中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所侍奉之青龙{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之澄境蕴风云{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩风飞速聚集{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明前之朦月{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意互通{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南风之弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.49,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是沙威鲁德前辈所说的ChaosChoir的拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是前所未有的可怕的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.59,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来干得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.14,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们潜藏着超乎我们想象的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.20,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得越来越注意他们两个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上保重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再乱跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后我们永远一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得太好了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们已经是命运共同体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论前面有着多么严酷的考验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天涯海角我们都携手共行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.62,0:22:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在理想与现实的夹缝中生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论想选择哪一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 追忆的子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随着枪声响起 少女失去了温情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:23:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六唱 追忆的子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:33.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえばここには愛すべき声があって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:39.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あたしはそれすら守らなくて{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:48.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月雨　街を照らす黄昏{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.28,0:13:56.94,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　隠した思い出に染まってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さよならだなんて夢ならいいって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴れない心模様{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨ならやむってニュースが言ってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう　行かなくちゃ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:38.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事な事ほど目に映らない法則{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:45.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あたしは今さら悔いたりして{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.81,0:14:54.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩　移り行く紫陽花{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:15:02.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ　記憶を憂鬱になぞってる{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あどけないままのあの日の愛を{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れていいのかな{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.87,0:15:15.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頬濡らす雫　乾いてゆく{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら行かなくちゃ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉を越えたつもりでいた{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれは夢だった？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.94,0:15:58.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慣れた体温を探してないよ{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう行けるでしょう？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さよならだなんて夢ならいいって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴れない心模様{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふと飛び越えた水たまりに{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　空の色{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:27.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえばここには愛すべき声があって{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:34.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あたしはそれすら守らなくて{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:33.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,或许 这里有恋人的声音{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:39.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,而我 却连那也守护不了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:48.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,梅雨中 夕阳照耀着街道{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.28,0:13:56.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,浸染那深藏于心的回忆{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,“分手只是一场梦该多好”{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,愁绪无法释怀{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,预报说雨快停了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,好了 该出发了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:38.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,越重要的东西 却越无法映入眼帘{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:45.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,我 现在才开始后悔{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.81,0:14:54.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,花色渐变的紫阳花{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:15:02.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,记忆仍带着忧郁的痕迹{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,天真烂漫的昔日之爱{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,是否可以忘记{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.87,0:15:15.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,脸颊上的水滴 已逐渐干去{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,嗯 该出发了{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.98,0:15:50.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,曾感到你我之间无需言语{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,那只是南柯一梦吗？{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.94,0:15:58.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,我已不再探寻你那熟悉的体温{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,已经 可以离去了吧{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.68,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,“分手只是一场梦该多好”{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,愁绪无法释怀{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,不经意间跃过的水坑中{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,看 倒映着天空的颜色{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:27.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,或许 这里有恋人的声音{\an9}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.95,0:16:34.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0030,,而我 却连那也守护不了{\an9}
